*while: 0 < 1
	*clear
	
	*question: Email address to test:
		*type: text
		*save: email

	Validating...

	>> betterEmailValidationInput = email
	*program: Better Email Validation

	*if: betterEmailValidationOutput = "yes"
		*component
			*classes: alert alert-success
			The email address "{email}" is valid!

	*if: betterEmailValidationOutput = "no"
		*component
			*classes: alert alert-danger
			The email address "{email}" is invalid! {betterEmailValidationFailMessage}

	*button: Validate another address
